Module ATM

Class Account

java.lang.Object
Account
public class Account extends Object
Represents the following bank account information:
Account number
Available balance
Name of the account holder
Total balance and available balance
ATM pin number of the account holder

      theTotalBalance - Total balance, including the pending transaction
